    "description": "漫畫為許多創作的源頭，漫畫創作有著各式各樣繪製方式、繪畫風格與創意。本課程透過創意激盪、創作意念表達，經過不斷的分鏡練習、繪圖技法練習以及完稿練習，期望學生配合生活、時事話題或是現實觀察等等議題，並不斷動筆繪製，最終讓學生完成漫畫作品。<br>",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.話題激盪/幻想/時事/社會思考<br>2.分鏡練習<br>3.構圖思考<br>4.角色設計<br>5.分頁/分鏡/草稿<br>6.漫畫完稿",
        "en": "Practice and complete the comic:<br>1. Write a comic story: practice adapting the comic external compositional structure(ECS), development and controlling the progress of the ECS<br>2. Create a background for the character: Analyze how the role background affects the character's design when creating different roles<br>3. Comic character design: learning to draw a variety of different roles<br>4. Character performance: practice to express stories with different expressions and body movements<br>5. Comic Splitter: Practice splitting the screen according to the plot to express the character's emotions and stories<br>6. Split draft: draw a clear draft of the split as a reference for the final draft"
    },
